### Platform Schema

```json
{
  "id": "string (unique identifier)",
  "name": "string (Korean name)",
  "nameEn": "string (English name)",
  "description": "string (service description)",
  "url": "string (main page URL)",
  "categories": "string[] (category IDs)",
